## 5.2   测试流程

### 5.2.1 新增特性测试

1. vhost-user-blk磁盘随机读写

虚拟机vhost-user-blk xml配置：
```
<disk type='vhostuser' device='disk'>
  <driver queues='4'/>
  <source type='unix' path='/var/tmp/vhost.0'>
    <reconnect enabled='yes' timeout='3'/>
  </source>
  <target dev='vdb' bus='virtio'/>
</disk>
```

多线程随机读：
```
fio -bs=4k -ioengine=libaio -iodepth=128 -numjobs=64 -direct=1 -rw=randread -time_based -runtime=30 -refill_buffers -norandommap -randrepeat=0 -group_reporting -name=fio-randread-iops -size=10G -filename=/dev/xxx
```

多线程随机写：
```
fio -bs=4k -ioengine=libaio -iodepth=128 -numjobs=64 -direct=1 -rw=randwrite -time_based -runtime=30 -refill_buffers -norandommap -randrepeat=0 -group_reporting -name=fio-randread-iops -size=10G -filename=/dev/xxx
```


